commit.message:
unwind-c.c: Add libgcc-style exception.

	* unwind-c.c: Add libgcc-style exception.
	* unwind-dw2.c: Likewise.
	* unwind-pe.h: Likewise.
	* unwind-sjlj.c: Likewise.
	* unwind.inc: Likewise.

From-SVN: r70576

files.patch:

+2003-08-19  Daniel Jacobowitz  <drow@mvista.com>
+
+	* unwind-c.c: Add libgcc-style exception.
+	* unwind-dw2.c: Likewise.
+	* unwind-pe.h: Likewise.
+	* unwind-sjlj.c: Likewise.
+	* unwind.inc: Likewise.
+
